title: [Zzentar's Magic Shoppe]
[Zzentar's Combat Gear]
[Zzentar's General Store]
description: Smooth granite walls rise from an enameled hardwood floor.  Just above a worn rug hangs a tattered merchant permit, and a vaulted ceiling completes the picture.  A wicker basket and a gold-leafed mistwood cabinet stand side by side in the middle of the room.
